description:
She is an unnamed high school upperclassman who is the president of disciplinary committee. She cannot stand http://anidb.net/ch89068 [Yoshiko]`s idiocy. When http://anidb.net/ch89069 [Akuru] starts complimenting her by accident, she develops a major crush on Akuru - she starts stalking him, and often has lewd fantasies about him.
Yoshiko considers her a rival because of the girl`s large breast size. In many instances she tries to reach out to Akuru but her interactions give her a reputation of being just as weird, even though she is unaware of that. She is fairly smart academically, placing in the top 5 of her class.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Fuuki Iinchou
